{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"62be1b892b","title":"在中共武汉市委召开的座谈会上的发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d5b02dbb54","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":5,"articleId":"62be1b892b"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5ebc145740","name":"刘叔模"},{"id":"f46655e252","name":"湖北"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f8be4cc735","type":"title","text":"在中共武汉市委召开的座谈会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"},{"id":"b3d0fd26b7","type":"authors","text":"湖北刘叔模","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"},{"id":"375e79fc84","type":"subtitle","text":"（按：刘叔模现任民革武汉市委会秘书长、武汉市人民委员会参事室参事。以下是他在鸣放期间发表的一系列右派言论的一部分。）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"},{"id":"2e82bbc020","type":"paragraph","text":"刘叔模说，“墙”“沟”的问题主要是宗派主义，旧社会讲权势，有的靠权势无所不为，有的厌权势有所不为。解放以后我有一种感觉，仿佛有人多接近党员就是靠拢党，靠拢党的人可能是无所不为的人，而党说他们是积极分子，形成宗派主义。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"},{"id":"5a3090aead","type":"paragraph","text":"刘叔模建议重大问题应由党和民主党派协商，民主党派的领导干部应由民主党派民主选举，以便更好的发挥民主党派的作用。（见6月5日“长江日报”）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"},{"id":"a2382d8fdd","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（湖北人民出版社，1957年9月）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b"}],"page":{"id":"8e6418eeaa","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"62be1b892b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}